cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MS, cs.MM

The paper deals with the segmentation of ultrasound scans of arteries using Convolutional Neural Networks, specifically U-Net with VGG16 encoder. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep learning techniques for segmentation also falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves medical imaging (cs.MS) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with the analysis of intravascular ultrasound images.
